We invite you to visit our profile @iavaarts
The International Association of Visual Artists is a non-profit organization, the main purpose is to protect the rights and promote the interests of all its members as visual artists,started in Florence - Italy in 2013. The organization currently has members in 27 countries.
For more details of IAVA, send to us an email to contact@iavaarts.org
